### 6. Compliance Summary

- **SC 3.3.2 (Labels or Instructions)**: Required indicator + labels on all fields
- **SC 4.1.1 (Parsing)**: Valid HTML, no duplicate IDs, proper nesting
- **SC 4.1.2 (Name, Role, Value)**: All form controls have accessible names
