3. **Drush Command to Audit PDF Accessibility (SC 1.4.5, 1.4.12)**
   ```bash
   drush php:script scripts/check-pdf-acs.php --path=/var/www/html
   ```
   Where `scripts/check-pdf-acs.php`:
   ```php
   <?php
   use Drupal\file\Entity\File;
   $files = File::loadMultiple();
   foreach ($files as $file) {
     if ($file->getMimeType() === 'application/pdf') {
       $path = $file->getFileUri();
       $real_path = str_replace('public://', 'public://', $path);
       if (!file_exists($real_path)) continue;
       $output = shell_exec("pdftotext \"$real_path\" - 2>&1");
       if (empty($output)) {
         drush_log("Empty or non-text PDF: {$file->getFilename()}", 'warning');
       } else {
         drush_log("Text-extractable PDF: {$file->getFilename()}", 'ok');
       }
     }
   }
   ```

