     $build['#attributes']['role'] = 'dialog';
     $build['#attributes']['aria-modal'] = 'true';
     $build['#attributes']['aria-labelledby'] = 'permit-modal-title';
     $build['#prefix'] = '<div id="permit-modal" class="modal hidden">';
     $build['#suffix'] = '</div>';
     ```

2. **Twig Template (`modal.html.twig`)**
   ```twig
